Package: universalaccel
Type: Package
Title: Universal Accelerometer Summary Metrics
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jimmy Duhamahoro", email = "jimmydhr1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reproducible pipeline to load, calibrate, and summarize raw accelerometer data
    from ActiGraph, Axivity, and GENEActiv. Computes MIMS, Activity Index (AI), ENMO,
    MAD, ROCAM, and ActiGraph activity counts with optional Choi non-wear flags.
